Hey there!

I’m the lead programmer on team FYRE, 5480. We recently, got our new roboRIO for the 2025 season. We wanted to use it for some off-season practice. I loaded it up with the latest 2024 firmware, and tried it out. I connected to our new radio just fine, but driverstation didn’t have any contact with the roborio. We swapped radios just to be sure, still nothing. We tried last years roborio, and it worked fine for both radios. Reflashing the firmware also did nothing.

Is anyone else having this issue? How should we go about remedying it?
Any help is greatly appreciated. Thanks.
